data.description: Welcome home to 7862 Red Birch Circle. The home has one of the largest lots in the Summerfield neighborhood and no H.O.A.! The home boast a combination of hardwood and engineered flooring throughout most of the living areas. The kitchen has a brand new stainless steel refrigerator and range. There is also a front room over the garage that could be used as a fourth bedroom, office or family room.  The home also includes a spacious sunroom for relaxing or entertaining guests . In addition, there is a large 2 car detached garage with space for a workshop. This home is close to Bosch, Boeing, Mercedes factories, local outlets and malls.
